s. This equation resembles a half-circle when plotted on the y-axis, then submerged on the xy plane/world, appearing as half-submerged. The design serves as a creative interpretation blending cultural symbolism with mathematical concepts, suitable for use as an installation piece.\n\nYou can also check the design on my [TikTok](https://www.tiktok.com/@arnottferels/photo/7333888833131400454).\n\n<div className=\"mdx-gd4-gview\">\n  <ImgDefa>![Half-submerged](./figures/half-submerged-01.png \"Half-submerged\")</ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>![Half-submerged](./figures/half-submerged-02.png \"Half-submerged\")</ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>![Half-submerged](./figures/half-submerged-03.png \"Half-submerged\")</ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>![Half-submerged](./figures/half-submerged-04.png \"Half-submerged\")</ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>![Half-submerged](./figures/half-submerged-05.png \"Half-submerged\")</ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>![Half-submerged](./figures/half-submerged-06.png \"Half-submerged\")</ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>![Half-submerged](./figures/half-submerged-07.png \"Half-submerged\")</ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>![Half-submerged](./figures/half-submerged-08.png \"Half-submerged\")</ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>![Half-submerged](./figures/half-submerged-09.png \"Half-submerged\")</ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>![Half-submerged](./figures/half-submerged-10.png \"Half-submerged\")</ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>![Half-submerged](./figures/half-submerged-11.png \"Half-submerged\")</ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>![Half-submerged](./figures/half-submerged-12.png \"Half-submerged\")</ImgDefa>\n</div>\n","tableOfContents":{}}},"pageContext":{"id":"24276e20-c2ca-53db-b0c8-cc99b1e75397","frontmatter__p_type":"models","frontmatter__slug":"half-submerged","__params":{"frontmatter__p_type":"models","frontmatter__slug":"half-submerged"},"frontmatter":{"p_type":"models","title":"Half-submerged","slug":"half-submerged","date":"2023-12","hero_img_src":"./figures/half-submerged-01.png","hero_img_alt":"Half-submerged","hero_img_crd_txt":"Arnott Ferels","hero_i